title: Spacious 3 Bed 2 Bath Single Family Home
posting_body: ['2348 113th Ave NW Coon Rapids, Minnesota 55433', 'Price: $1800.00', 'Deposit : $1800.00', 'Large 3 bed, 2 bath home located near Coon Rapids HS, Riverdale Shopping area and local parks and trails.', 'Upon entering you’ll fall in love with the hardwood floors throughout the main floor+ luxury flooring in kitchen.', 'Kitchen provides direct access to newly built double deck, perfect for the upcoming spring and summer for those who want to unwind with their favorite cocktail or start their morning with a cup of coffee.', 'You’ll find 2 bedrooms on the main floor as well as an updated bathroom.', 'Bonus dining area or office/den also located off the kitchen.', 'Finished LL basement provides added living space along with 1 BR, an additional office and a ¾ bath.', 'Large shed+ double car garage are perfect for storage and keeping your car free of snow this winter.', 'Avail September 9th- 12 or 18 month lease terms.', 'Tenant pays all utilities  and responsible for snow+lawn care.', 'No pets allowed.', 'Information deemed reliable but not guaranteed.', 'Renters insurance required & must list owners as additional insured.', 'Section 8 not approved.', 'Pet Policy: No pets allowed.', 'Property Features', 'Single Family Home', '3 bed', '2 bath', 'Built 1961', '2 Parking Spaces', 'Land is 0.23 square', 'Floor Area is 1,730 square', '2 Garage', 'Ducted Heating', 'Ducted Cooling', 'Anoka County', 'Ceiling Fan', 'deck', 'Detached Garage', 'Hardwood Floors', 'Kitchen Window', 'Natural Woodwork', 'School District 11', 'Storage Shed', 'Visit our website at <URL> for more information.']
